      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"6. CHAROS DREAM held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a nose (17.60) behind Boom Striker at this track. Racing well and deserves a win. 7. FIRE UP FROG is having her first start around this course. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 10 lengths (23.46) at Mandurah. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to feature in the finish. 8. FUNNY FINNY had been racing well without winning, recording three minors on end before copping a check in the run and finishing seventh in a Novice race at Cannington (22.81). Worth following up. 2. MISS MAKUTZ warrants respect although new to this track.\",\"runners\":[6,7,8,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
